---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service — CloakShare" description="CloakShare terms of service." canonical="/terms">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-4xl text-foreground mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Acceptance</h2>
          <p>
            By using CloakShare ("the Service"), you agree to these terms. If you don't agree,
            don't use the Service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">The Service</h2>
          <p>
            CloakShare provides secure document and video sharing via API. You upload files, we render
            them into secure viewer links with tracking, watermarks, and access controls. The software
            is open source under the MIT License.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Your responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>You own the content you upload, or have the right to share it.</li>
            <li>You won't use the Service to share illegal, harmful, or infringing content.</li>
            <li>You're responsible for keeping your API keys and credentials secure.</li>
            <li>You won't attempt to circumvent usage limits or rate limits.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Our responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>We'll make reasonable efforts to keep the Service available and secure.</li>
            <li>We won't access your uploaded files except to provide the Service or when required by law.</li>
            <li>We'll notify you of material changes to these terms.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Billing</h2>
          <p>
            Paid plans are billed monthly via Stripe. You can cancel anytime. Refunds are handled
            on a case-by-case basis. The free tier includes limited usage — see the
            <a href="/pricing" class="text-accent hover:underline">pricing page</a> for details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Termination</h2>
          <p>
            You can delete your account at any time. We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate
            these terms. On termination, your files and rendered content are permanently deleted.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Liability</h2>
          <p>
            The Service is provided "as is" without warranty. We're not liable for indirect, incidental,
            or consequential damages. Our total liability is limited to the amount you've paid us in the
            12 months prior.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:legal@cloakshare.dev" class="text-accent hover:underline">legal@cloakshare.dev</a>
            or open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/cloakshare/cloakshare" class="text-accent hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
